Project: PostgreSQL Backup Manager
Version: 1.0.0 (Beta)
Status: In Development & Testing
Author: Michael BAG
Email: mk@remark.pro
Telegram: https://t.me/michaelbag

Description:
Script application for automatic backup of PostgreSQL databases with support for:
- Multiple backup formats (custom, plain)
- Backup compression
- Remote storage (FTP, WebDAV, CIFS/Samba)
- Multi-database configuration
- Automatic cleanup of old backups
- Detailed logging

Development Status:
- Core functionality: Complete
- Testing phase: In progress
- Production ready: No (Beta version)
- Stability: Under active development

